Package: iLaplace
Type: Package
Title: Improved Laplace Approximation for Marginal Likelihoods
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2015-09-01
Authors@R: c(
       person("Erlis", "Ruli", email = "erlisr@yahoo.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
       person("Nicola", "Sartori", role = "aut"),
       person("Laura", "Ventura", role = "aut"))
Description: Improved Laplace approximation for integrals of concave and unimodal functions. The method requires user-supplied R functions for: the integrand, its gradient and its Hessian matrix. The computations are run in parallel.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2), stats
Imports: doParallel, parallel, plyr, Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: devtools
License: GPL-2
URL:  https://github.com/erlisR/iLaplace
BugReports:  https://github.com/erlisR/iLaplace/issues
Author: Erlis Ruli [aut, cre], Nicola Sartori [aut], Laura Ventura [aut]
Maintainer: Erlis Ruli <erlisr@yahoo.it>
LazyData: true
